item.title: What I really know ?
item.description: I have been programming for almost 7 years, and in this time I have got a Bacholor’s in Computer Science and a Master’s in Computer Science build a few apps worked on few backend projects and ML too but at the end what do I really know ? I know HTML, CSS and JS but no react or react-native. I know Flutter but not very well I know backend but ony with Python and Django
